comments: I've been doing this workout for about a month. I'm 61 years old. Yesterday I shoveled snow for 4.5 hrs. Today I feel fine. I love Calimove.
One of the best calisthenics channels on the internet.
Can we just appreciate that  El Eggs, the dude who can do planche push ups, backflips, and splits laying on the couch with junk food and a remote control is the funniest thing ever?

3 circuits of 5 exercises (20min)
30sec exercise - 60sec rest
- Push-ups (—inclined push ups)
- Jumping-squats (++jump higher)
- Rows (—decrease range of motion, bending knees)
- Shifting knee up
- Swimmer (++use weights)
